Following the approval of the relevant Change Advisory Board (CAB) request, please be advised of the upcoming planned maintenance activity affecting the production instance of **Bitbucket Server**.

**Activity:**
Migration of the Bitbucket production database from **Microsoft SQL Server 2016** to **Microsoft SQL Server 2022**.

**Maintenance Window:**
[DATE] from [START TIME] to [END TIME]

**Affected Services:**

* Bitbucket Production Server
* Jenkins pipelines dependent on Bitbucket repositories

During the maintenance window, the Bitbucket service will be **fully stopped prior to the start of the activity**. As a result, the following operations will be temporarily unavailable:

* Repository access via the Bitbucket web interface
* Git operations (clone, pull, push)
* Jenkins pipelines that retrieve source code from Bitbucket

Once the database migration and restoration activities are completed, the Bitbucket service will be restarted and validated. The **estimated restoration and service verification time is approximately one hour**.

A completion notification will be shared once the maintenance activity has concluded and services have been successfully restored.

